OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny remaining overnight rain in
OL,6,Fsouth soon clearing. Then a dry day
OL,7,Fwith some good spells of sunshine, but
OL,8,Fturning hazier later in the afternoon
OL,9,Fas cloud spills east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first but cloud and a
OL,12,Ffew light showers spreading east
OL,13,Fthrough the evening. Cloudy for all
OL,14,Fparts overnight with some showery rain
OL,15,Fspreading southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
