OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,6,Fsoutheast. Then mostly dry with sunny
OL,7,Fspells and just the odd shower in the
OL,8,Fnorth. Showers become heavier and more
OL,9,Ffrequent later. Blustery northwest
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,13,Fcold Wednesday with heavy showers and
OL,14,Foccasionally strong northwesterly
OL,15,Fwinds, the showers and winds easing on
OL,16,FThursday. Mostly dry, bright on Friday
OL,17,Fbut chance of evening rain in
OL,18,Fnorthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
